            <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/sports/columns">COLUMNS</a></span></div>

                <h1>When the time is right</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/eb7d7855-befe-4b52-85c8-3010fdb9736c.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Patience&#x20;is&#x20;a&#x20;virtue&#x3A;&#x20;Duke&#x20;stuck&#x20;with&#x20;David&#x20;Cutcliffe&#x20;after&#x20;a&#x20;rough&#x20;first&#x20;few&#x20;seasons,&#x20;and&#x20;both&#x20;Virginia&#x20;Tech&#x2019;s&#x20;Frank&#x20;Beamer&#x20;&#x28;left&#x29;&#x20;and&#x20;Miami&#x2019;s&#x20;Al&#x20;Golden&#x20;&#x28;right&#x29;&#x20;have&#x20;struggled&#x20;with&#x20;traditional&#x20;powerhouses&#x20;in&#x20;recent&#x20;years.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Patience is a virtue: Duke stuck with David Cutcliffe after a rough first few seasons, and both Virginia Tech’s Frank Beamer (left) and Miami’s Al Golden (right) have struggled with traditional powerhouses in recent years.</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/darbi-griffith">Darbi Griffith</a> |
                                                                                                                                The Chronicle
                                                                            </figcaption>
                                </aside>
                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/sameer-pandhare">Sameer Pandhare</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">October 20, 2015 | 12:17am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
